        <StoryText>
            <text>
In  the  faraway  land  of  Erivion,  the  Dark  Lord  Sreep
has  risen  to  ruthless  power  and  is  spreading  his  reign
of  terror and  destruction  whenever  he  sets  his  gaze.
In  the midst  of  the  chaos  you,  an  intrepid  albeit
young  mercenary  mage by  the  name  of  Stuart  Dent,
have  arrived  on  scene  to  put  an  end  to
the  Dark  Lord's  reign, and  acquire  the  fortune
and  glory  of  heroism.
It  is  up  to  you  to  save  the  world!  Good  Luck!
